// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/DddyWr triagonal oriented random blocks, by jt
// based on https://www.shadertoy.com/view/ds3cWn random rotated triangles checker
// based on of https://www.shadertoy.com/view/DljBDm three directions city grid patch
// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/dtBBRw three dir grid patches essence
// 2d essence of https://www.shadertoy.com/view/DtsBWl three directional grid patches

// Loopless random blocks oriented in three directions.
// For interesting placement of buildings in procedurally generated city maps than just rectangular grid,
// while at the same time being reasonably easy addressable, for grid-based simulation and wayfinding.
// The underlying triangular structure facilitates seamless inclusion of terrain (via heightmap & triangle mesh).

// Algorithm:
// For each triangle in tiling choose (1 of 3) directions randomly.
// If orientation matches neighbor triangle color half-triangle with direction color.
// Apply fourth color to unmatched half triangles.

// Alternates between independent triangles and triangles grouped to hexagons.
// Click to show underlying triangular grid.

// tags: procedural, 2d, rectangles, grid, grid, triangle, triangles, patterns, random, rectangle, barycentric, city, pattern, hex, grids

